<item>
            <title>[LU-4354] 2.1 clients fail to mount upgraded 2.4 filesystem with EEXIST</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4354</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Clients are unable to mount an ldiskfs filesystem upgraded from 2.1 to 2.4.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Transcribed client messages:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mgc_request.c:247 do_config_log_add() failed processing sptlrpc log: -2
genops.c:304 class_newdev() ls4-OST0000-osc-... alread exists, won&apos;t add
obd_config.c:368:class_attach() Cannot create defvice ls4-OST000... of type osc: -17
obd_config.c:1491:class_config_llog_handler() Err -17 on cfg command:
 cmd=cf001 0:ls4-OST0000... 1:osc 2:ls4-clilov_UUID
LustreError: The configuration from log &apos;ls4-client&apos; failed (-17). ...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="22360">LU-4354</key>
            <summary>2.1 clients fail to mount upgraded 2.4 filesystem with EEXIST</summary>
